01:21:45,126 --> 01:21:47,292
Iron-Fist Ngai Ba-tin vs Wing Chun's Wong Tung

1058
01:21:50,751 --> 01:21:53,042
King, babysit for me.

1059
01:22:01,042 --> 01:22:01,667
Sei Mui!

