Beat him up...

1087
01:24:30,001 --> 01:24:31,209
Beat him up...

1088
01:24:33,751 --> 01:24:34,709
Halt!

1089
01:24:35,001 --> 01:24:35,876
Ignore him!

1090
01:24:35,876 --> 01:24:36,459
Carry on!

1091
01:24:38,042 --> 01:24:38,917
